#: changes.rst:1935
msgid ""
"Python 3.12 is now supported, though not recommended, see :ref:`python-deps`."
msgstr ""
"Python 3.12 ahora está mantenido, aunque no está recomendado, "
"consulte :ref:`python-deps`."

