msgid "*Released on December 16th 2021.*"
msgstr "*Publicada el 16 de diciembre de 2021.*"

#: changes/v4.rst:525
msgid "Added support for formality and placeholders with DeepL."
msgstr ""
"Se agregó compatibilidad con niveles de formalidad y sustitutivos con DeepL."

#: changes/v4.rst:526
msgid ""
"Bulk edit and search-and-replace are now available on project and language "
