"Many of the tests in the Weblate test suite use the test repository. The "
"test suite repository is maintained at https://github.com/WeblateOrg/test. "
"The script :file:`scripts/pack-test-data.sh` is then used to generate a "
"tarball with a repository for each of the supported version control systems. "
"These are stored as :file:`weblate/trans/tests/data/test-base-"
"repo.git.tar`, :file:`weblate/trans/tests/data/test-base-repo.hg.tar`, "
"and :file:`weblate/trans/tests/data/test-base-repo.svn.tar` in the Weblate "
