"WeblateOrg/test. El script :file:`scripts/pack-test-data.sh` se utiliza para "
"generar un archivo tar con un repositorio para cada uno de los sistemas de "
"control de versiones compatibles. Estos se almacenan como :file:`weblate/"
"trans/tests/data/test-base-repo.git.tar`, :file:`weblate/trans/tests/data/"
"test-base-repo.hg.tar` y :file:`weblate/trans/tests/data/test-base-"
"repo.svn.tar` en el repositorio de Weblate."

#: contributing/tests.rst:137
msgid ""
"The https://github.com/WeblateOrg/test repository is tagged at the release "
"time, which ensures that the release tags can be used to access test data "
"used at the release time. The script tries to create reproducible tarballs "
"as much as possible."
